    <lb n="56"/>ᾐτιάσατο δὲ καὶ Ἡλιόδωρον <app type="BL"><lem resp="cf. 1.210">ἐπὶ ἀγνωμοσύ<unclear reason="undefined">νῃ</unclear></lem><rdg>ἐ<unclear reason="undefined">π</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ωσεωσ</rdg></app> 

    <lb n="57"/>μέτρου <app type="BL"><lem resp="cf. 1.210">ἐλαίου</lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost">δ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">ικαί</unclear>ου</rdg></app>. κεινη<unclear reason="undefined">θεὶς</unclear> <app type="BL"><lem resp="cf. 1.210">τῇ ἐξου<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied>ίᾳ</lem><rdg><unclear reason="undefined">διὰ</unclear>  <choice><corr>ἐξουσία<supplied reason="omitted">ς</supplied></corr><sic>εξου<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied>ια</sic></choice></rdg></app> τοῦ κυρίου μο<supplied reason="lost">υ</supplied> 

    <lb n="58"/>τοῦ λαμπροτάτου ἡγεμόνος <expan>Φλ<ex>αουίου</ex></expan> Ἡρακλείου π<unclear reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="3" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">ι</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">ι</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/> διὰ τῆς τάξεως καὶ αὐτὸν <supplied reason="omitted">τὸν</supplied> Παχῦμιν καὶ 

